#if soper
Command provided by: nickserv/set_notifyset
#endif
Help for SET NOTIFYSET:

If enabled, get notified whenever your group or
channel settings in channels where you're on the ACL
changes.

The notification will come in the form of a private
notice, as well as a memo, if possible.

NOTE: Whether you will in fact get a notification
    depends on the settings of the channel.

Syntax: SET NOTIFYSET [ON|OFF]

Example:
    /msg &nick& SET NOTIFYSET ON